Quickscene: Lightning-Fast Video Search System
SuperBryn Technical Assessment

This project demonstrates enterprise-level software development practices
including modern architecture, performance optimization, comprehensive
testing, and production deployment strategies.

Built with:
- OpenAI Whisper for speech recognition
- SentenceTransformers for semantic embeddings  
- FAISS for vector similarity search
- FastAPI for high-performance backend
- React TypeScript for modern frontend
- Professional deployment infrastructure

Author: Sandeep Kumar Sahoo
Email: sandeep.savethem2@gmail.com
GitHub: https://github.com/MrDecryptDecipher/Quickscene
